                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature successfully cauterizes one of the prismhydra's stumps</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The unstable prismatic energies in the prismhydra's body surge forth. Each creature adjacent to the prismhydra is exposed to its chromatic explosion.</p>"
